Reasoning: The paper discusses the longitudinal development of patent classifications in material technologies for photovoltaic cells, and the use of cyclical patterns to indicate technological life-cycles. This suggests a focus on information retrieval (IR) and data mining (DL) techniques for analyzing patent data. The paper also discusses the use of visualization techniques, which could fall under the sub-category of social and information networks (SI). Additionally, the paper touches on the role of inventors in the development of technology, which could relate to the sub-categories of cybernetics (CY) and systems and control (SD).
